HELIXos Contributor Toolkit — attribution
==========================================

The contents of this .claude/ directory are adapted from operator-kit:

    operator-kit — https://github.com/wrg32786/operator-kit
    Copyright (c) wrg32786
    Licensed under the MIT License.

What was taken from operator-kit:
  - The concept of five specialist Claude Code subagents (design, build, scout,
    research, critique).
  - The idea of a UserPromptSubmit context-loader hook driven by a keyword ->
    files JSON configuration.

What is original to HELIXos:
  - The agent prompts in agents/helix/ are rewritten for this repository, renamed
    to the HELIXos deity taxonomy (PTAH, OGUN, ARGUS, THOTH, ATHENA), and scoped
    to its architecture and honesty constraints.
  - The context-loader hook (hooks/helix-context-loader.sh and
    hooks/helix_context_loader.py) is an independent re-implementation; no
    operator-kit code was copied.
  - The keyword configuration (helix-keywords.json) targets HELIXos files.

